---

<Layout title="Nicholas Charriere" showHome={false}>
  <h1 class="text-4xl mt-4 mb-6 font-bold">Nicholas Charriere</h1>
  <p class="max-w-xl">
    I like to build things and I care a lot about craft. I'm optimistic about
    technology and what it can do for the world. Currently working on
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://getmocha.com">Mocha</a
    >{" "}with{" "}

    <a
