  </p>
  <p class="max-w-xl pt-8 sm:pt-6">
    I recently was a founding engineer at{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://privy.io">Privy</a
    >. Before that I spent 4 years on the ML platform team at{" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://getcruise.com">Cruise</a
    >, 2 years at {" "}
    <a
      class="text-text-700 font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="https://pinterest.com">Pinterest</a
