  </p>
  <div class="pt-8 flex flex-col items-start gap-1">
    <a
      class="text-text-700 text-xl font-medium underline hover:text-froly-500 transition-all duration-200 hover:no-underline underline-offset-2"
      href="/blog"
    >
      Blog
